\item symbolic comparison  condition generalized from comparing   $LR_{[i]}$ and with all $LI_{[j]}$ :\\
$\mathsf{symbCaseI}(LR,LI,i)\equiv $\\
\begin{numcases}{ }
   symbCmp(LR,LI,i,j)& if $\exists! j.  LR_{[i]}=LI_{[j]}$\\
   forallForm(|LI|,pf)& otherwise
 \end{numcases}
